# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Data, results and large binaries — not tracked in git
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
/backup
/Data
/Resultater
/Møder
/Præsentationer

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Office / document files
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
*.docx
*.doc
*.pptx
*.ppt
*.xlsx
*.xls

# PDF files — exclude generated/report PDFs
